## Critical Notes

### 1️⃣ API keys are hardcoded

Inject keys via initializer or secure storage.

### 2️⃣ Batch is not real batch

OpenAI batch → one assistant response.

### 3️⃣ Model selection is inconsistent

Some paths ignore `model.rawValue`.

### 4️⃣ Grok is a stub

Routes to OpenAI fallback.

